menu "XIAO ESP32-S3 options"

    config XIAO_EXTERNAL_ANTENNA
        bool "Enable external U.FL antenna (XIAO ESP32-S3 Sense, GPIO14)"
        default n
        help
            Drive GPIO14 HIGH to route RF through the external U.FL connector
            instead of the built-in PCB antenna.
            Only needed on the XIAO ESP32-S3 Sense variant when an external
            antenna is physically attached.

endmenu
